PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue to amend the Proclamation authorizing the minting of a series of four PLATINUM COLLECTORS' COINS in denominations of $30, $75, $150 and $300 featuring a WOOD BISON BULL, in order to make the $150 platinum coin's description more precise.

precis:
Order directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue to amend the Proclamation
authorizing the minting of a series of four PLATINUM COLLECTORS' COINS in
denominations of $30, $75, $150 and $300 featuring a WOOD BISON BULL, in
order to make the $150 platinum coin's description more precise.
